          <div class="info">
            My name is David Tran, a first generation Asian American. I have a wide variety of interests ranging from cooking, snowboarding, welding, gaming, and hundreds of other things that I want to eventually pick up. Most of which developed from my previous jobs - a chef, welder, commercial driver, English teacher, grocery stocker. For 9 years of my life after high school, I simply worked. But I just wanted more.. A challenge, security, opportunities for growth, and software development seemed to offer all that and so much more.
          </div>
